549
00:53:48,960 --> 00:53:49,360
[SPEAKER_00] Zajednica.

550
00:53:49,920 --> 00:53:50,960
[SPEAKER_00] To je ono što komunicirate.

551
00:53:52,639 --> 00:53:54,719
