552
00:53:55,360 --> 00:53:56,400
[SPEAKER_00] A šta komunicirate?

553
00:53:57,840 --> 00:53:58,960
[SPEAKER_00] Komunicirate zajednicu.

554
00:53:59,199 --> 00:53:59,280
