556
00:54:00,239 --> 00:54:00,320
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

557
00:54:01,440 --> 00:54:02,639
[SPEAKER_00] Mi komuniciramo, mi smo.

558
00:54:02,880 --> 00:54:07,360
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, nisi spomenuo ni tehnike, nisi spomenuo ni startupe, nisi spomenuo ništa drugo, rekao si zajednica.

559
00:54:07,519 --> 00:54:09,199
