593
00:57:22,480 --> 00:57:25,599
[SPEAKER_00] ali jako malo dolazi feedbacka sa te druge strane.

594
00:57:27,039 --> 00:57:29,920
[SPEAKER_00] Šta bi onda savjetovao content kreatorima?

595
00:57:31,679 --> 00:57:37,760
