645
01:01:41,119 --> 01:01:43,840
[SPEAKER_00] Da li si ti tu ili si više negdje dalje?

646
01:01:44,559 --> 01:01:44,880
[SPEAKER_00] Da li si.

647
01:01:45,280 --> 01:01:45,920
[SPEAKER_00] Da li za mamer?

648
01:01:46,320 --> 01:01:46,400
