660
01:03:11,599 --> 01:03:12,239
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje si ti?

661
01:03:12,320 --> 01:03:13,199
[SPEAKER_00] I koliko tih ljudi je?

662
01:03:13,519 --> 01:03:14,960
[SPEAKER_01] Super pitanje.

663
01:03:15,679 --> 01:03:18,400
[SPEAKER_01] Sad sam ja, rajan, Sean Evans, iskotvan sam o mediju.

664
01:03:18,960 --> 01:03:19,599
